{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.87\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">可拉後裔的詩歌。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">錫安頌</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.87.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>耶和華所立的根基在聖山上。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.87.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>耶和華愛<span class=\"pn\">錫安</span>的門，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">勝於愛<span class=\"pn\">雅各</span>一切的住處。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.87.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>上帝的城啊，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">有榮耀的事是指著你說的。（細拉）</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.87.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>我要提起<span class=\"pn\">拉哈伯</span>和<span class=\"pn\">巴比倫</span>人，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">是在認識我之中的；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\">看哪，<span class=\"pn\">非利士</span>、<span class=\"pn\">推羅</span>和<span class=\"pn\">古實</span>人，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">個個生在那裏。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.87.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>論到<span class=\"pn\">錫安</span>，必有話說：</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">「這一個、那一個都生在其中」；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">而且至高者必親自堅立這城。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.87.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>當耶和華記錄萬民的時候，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">他要寫出人的出生地。（細拉）</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.87.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup>歌唱的、跳舞的，都要說：</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">「我的泉源都在你裏面。」</span></p>\n</div>\n"}